01:24:20.707 --> 01:24:30.261
By this blood, Satan is going to ask that you should no more be kept his prisoner because you are a troublesome prisoner.

01:24:31.523 --> 01:24:41.618
Every form of captivity which has seized your life is broken today by the blood of the Lamb, the blood of Jesus Christ.

01:24:52.354 --> 01:24:53.536
with your hands for your blessing.

01:24:58.524 --> 01:25:10.402
Any chain on your leg, on your right leg, holding you down, is cursed and broken in Jesus.

01:25:12.685 --> 01:25:20.818
Any form of strangulation that is squeezing the air out of you slowly,

01:25:20.898 --> 01:25:24.604
built in Jesus' name.

01:25:24.624 --> 01:25:33.557
Any form of oppression and difficulty on your life, I reject it in Jesus' name.

01:25:33.577 --> 01:25:41.749
Every source of sadness in your life, every source of depression in your life, I cast it in Jesus' name.

01:25:41.769 --> 01:25:47.698
I command the spirit of joy to be released into your life.

01:25:49.122 --> 01:25:51.424
whatever has held you in captivity.

01:25:52.065 --> 01:26:03.457
For a long time, I decree by 31 December, you will hear the announcement that you are free forever from that captivity.

01:26:03.477 --> 01:26:05.059
Let me hear your loudest amen.

01:26:08.503 --> 01:26:16.451
The time has come for your freedom, for your joy, for your dancing, and for your liberation.

01:26:17.272 --> 01:26:18.994
Receive it in the name of Jesus.

01:26:20.130 --> 01:26:30.145
I declare that as God Almighty declared judgment on Pharaoh, on Egypt, on the economy of Egypt and on the gods of Egypt.

01:26:30.165 --> 01:26:37.676
So also there is a judgment on all the demonic forces and powers that have surrounded you and your life.

01:26:38.437 --> 01:26:40.480
Be delivered from it right now.

01:26:40.500 --> 01:26:43.745
In the name of Jesus.

01:26:43.765 --> 01:26:44.766
Become a giant.

01:26:45.567 --> 01:26:46.649
Become a champion.

01:26:47.230 --> 01:26:50.034
Become a great person because you are free.

01:26:50.818 --> 01:26:53.025
in the name of Jesus.

01:26:53.045 --> 01:26:54.229
Say I receive it.

01:26:55.533 --> 01:26:56.336
I walk in it.

01:26:56.376 --> 01:26:58.623
In the name of Jesus.

01:26:59.546 --> 01:27:01.231
Let me hear your loudest amen.

01:27:02.917 --> 01:27:04.562
God bless you, you may be seated.

